{"tid":824052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹過後深圳「四停」廣州「三停」 香港僅停課","createTime":"2018-09-17T02:49:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T03:03:07.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a97ad88a75934803e02e8089e5a396e0bb4676b7","tid":824052,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537147116_de0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537147116_de0d.jpg&h=8b2ae1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港昨日面對歷來最強大颱風「山竹」的挑戰，蹂躪本港10小時，多處地區包括柴灣、將軍澳、杏花邨及沙田出現海水倒灌，大量樹木倒塌阻塞馬路，有地盤天秤被吹至塌落隔鄰天台，超過362人在風暴中受傷，其中2人命危。不過在受「山竹」影響的地區紛紛宣佈停工、停課的同時，香港僅得教育局宣佈今日停課，但打工仔要照樣上班，令今日交通陷入癱瘓。<br />\n<br />\n廣州防颱總指揮部昨日發布「全民動員令」，宣佈全市範圍內實行「三停」，即停工、停產、停課。同時指揮部勒令全市各商務部門、商貿企業必須按照「三停」要求，立即執行停市，而全市商業企業、餐廳、門市、檔口等立即停止營業，確保市民的生命安全。<br />\n<br />\n深圳昨晚亦發出「防颱風防汛緊急動員令」，宣佈啟動全市防颱風和國家防汛應急響應級別Ⅰ級緊急響應。期間，深圳全市範圍內實行「四停」，即停工、停業、停市、停課。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於澳門，昨日就宣佈除救災部門等民防架構相關部門，以及駐外代表機構外，政府其餘部門今日關閉，公務人員毋須上班，而中小學、幼稚園和特殊教育學校今日亦全日停課。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180917/58690475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690475&d=GWino2b2s9Yv%2Fj0LkwBpODQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=76813c0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180917%2F58690475&h=3712f6af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180917/58690475</a><br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://i1.hoopchina.com.cn/hupuapp/bbs/335/61279514565335/thread_61279514565335_20180320114439_s_14480_o_h_197px_w_350px1125176340.jpeg?x-oss-process=image/resize,w_365/format,jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.hoopchina.com.cn%2Fhupuapp%2Fbbs%2F335%2F61279514565335%2Fthread_61279514565335_20180320114439_s_14480_o_h_197px_w_350px1125176340.jpeg%3Fx-oss-process%3Dimage%2Fresize%2Cw_365%2Fformat%2Cjpg&h=45d2374d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28e1ce972dc063f7cfb79ade63cbc2f4de1d80c6","tid":824052,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T03:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}